  "texts": [
    "We developed Med-PaLM, resulting in substantially improved physician evaluations over Flan-PaLM.",
    "However, evaluation on these benchmarks was limited as a measure of practical utility in real-world workflows, and key shortfalls remained compared to physician answers.",
    "Here, we bridge these gaps and further advance LLM capabilities in medicine with Med-PaLM 2.",
    "We developed this model using a combination of an improved base LLM (PaLM 2; ref.",
    "26), medical domain-specific fine-tuning and new prompting strategies to improve reasoning and grounding, including ensemble refinement and chain of retrieval."
  ],
